{"tid":1187251,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島（屋久島）幾問","createTime":"2019-06-05T13:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:27:50.000Z","uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46268b3786d4e28388ff1d55e0f285c59007b7d0","tid":1187251,"uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"黎緊月尾會去鹿兒島一帶玩十日<br />\n想問有冇人試過搭通宵船去屋企島<br />\n一來 又平d 同埋 想試下係船到睇日出＋星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但想問 女仔自己一個 會唔會唔方便<br />\n之前睇過其他post 話有女生專用室<br />\n但上網搵過 又唔多見有（其實通宵船既資料都少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c09c2abdb428d1e3dbf0e3d3f81dde10c259db","tid":1187251,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"直頭未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車都無通宵啦<br />\n𠵱啲島仔有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f9b91bd460ee2b7ecf438a61c4189977022079","tid":1187251,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"有錢咩都得"},{"pid":"76bc9db2d2ab729f5fdf4a548d7975befb9294be","tid":1187251,"uid":108418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"唔建議一個人去，都唔建議剩係去一兩日"},{"pid":"ee9605b330a55f3b1bbe80101f753ff8c71ec2d7","tid":1187251,"uid":108418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"喺香港行山都要兩個人以上，去到外地仲點會一個人行。要睇繩文杉最少預留四日喺島，無通宵船。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少座山，唔想喺新聞見到樓主。"},{"pid":"4d87022ad432f24ee8254b0ce48659ccfb5c2986","tid":1187251,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9605b330a55f3b1bbe80101f753ff8c71ec2d7","tid":1187251,"uid":108418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"喺香港行山都要兩個人以上，去到外地仲點會一個人行。要睇繩文杉最少預留四日喺島，無通宵船。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少座山，唔想喺新聞見到樓主。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"繩文杉點解要留咁耐？<br />\n來回九小時左右<br />\n行開山都應付到嘅<br />\n條路好明顯易行<br />\n係驚天氣唔好啫<br />\n樓主係好鐘意行山就留多幾日囉<br />\n<br />\n我就留咗三日兩夜<br />\n怕天氣唔好有啲位走<br />\n結果全好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab493fac20ceac519cabc32eef5036142dca9a0","tid":1187251,"uid":42271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"3-4日會好啲。夏天好易有颱風，屋久島更易中。無搭過通宵船，只搭過慢船，要4個鐘，但價錢平一半左右。"},{"pid":"8c4ef2e93ab562e3183f651fe59dfb6aa6522aa0","tid":1187251,"uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"原來大家都唔知就開心share下喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2170600/%E9%81%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B1%8B%E4%B9%85%E5%B3%B6%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E8%88%B9%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%9C%EF%BC%81%E6%9C%89%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%89%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%A9%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2170600%2F%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A9%2597%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%25AB%2583%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25A4%259C%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E6%25A9%259F&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a74924e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2170600/%E9%81%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B1%8B%E4%B9%85%E5%B3%B6%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E8%88%B9%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%9C%EF%BC%81%E6%9C%89%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%89%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%A9%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"847408a904ef30852280c13f4c6f34cca0f03a15","tid":1187251,"uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"咁我都冇話過 我只係留一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時就想 留四日左右<br />\n2日要黎行山露營 其餘都係想時間鬆動d 到時再決定做d咩好"},{"pid":"7f1cf55a7cfcd2aa98711a3d304715c1d737ac1d","tid":1187251,"uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab493fac20ceac519cabc32eef5036142dca9a0","tid":1187251,"uid":42271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"3-4日會好啲。夏天好易有颱風，屋久島更易中。無搭過通宵船，只搭過慢船，要4個鐘，但價錢平一半左右。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"想請教下 架船飄唔飄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會暈船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c89df5f6c19f051c343bee6c5c0473048ea37b","tid":1187251,"uid":42271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f1cf55a7cfcd2aa98711a3d304715c1d737ac1d","tid":1187251,"uid":138808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab493fac20ceac519cabc32eef5036142dca9a0","tid":1187251,"uid":42271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"3-4日會好啲。夏天好易有颱風，屋久島更易中。無搭過通宵船，只搭過慢船，要4個鐘，但價錢平一半左右。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"想請教下 架船飄唔飄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會暈船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"唔飄呀，事關個㗎船應該係貨船幾大下，4個鐘先到，一日得兩班，一來一回。客船就多好多，類似過澳門啲船咁，2個鐘就到。"},{"pid":"d10df61d94ce99fa1699826080f6b81bf44b3bdc","tid":1187251,"uid":220355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"如果住一晚夠唔夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}